<section class="guide-panel endgame-page" data-page="stat-endgame">
  <header class="panel-header">
    <span class="eyebrow">Stats finales</span>
    <h2>Reperes a viser</h2>
    <p class="lede">
      La Recharge d'energie reste le premier cap a verrouiller. Une fois ce
      seuil atteint, vise surtout taux critique, degats critiques, ATQ et bonus
      de degats Fusion.
    </p>
  </header>

  <div class="endgame-strip endgame-strip--editorial">
    <article class="endgame-stat">
      <div class="endgame-stat__head">
        <span class="endgame-stat__label">Recharge d'energie</span>
        <span class="endgame-stat__hint">Priorite</span>
      </div>
      <strong class="endgame-stat__value">115 - 125%+</strong>
      <p class="endgame-stat__note">
        Le bas de fourchette correspond a Lynae + Mornye, le haut a une equipe avec Jianxin + Mornye.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="endgame-stat">
      <div class="endgame-stat__head">
        <span class="endgame-stat__label">Taux critique</span>
      </div>
      <strong class="endgame-stat__value">65%+</strong>
      <p class="endgame-stat__note">Avant bonus de set.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="endgame-stat">
      <div class="endgame-stat__head">
        <span class="endgame-stat__label">Degats critiques</span>
      </div>
      <strong class="endgame-stat__value">210 - 260%+</strong>
    </article>

    <article class="endgame-stat">
      <div class="endgame-stat__head">
        <span class="endgame-stat__label">ATQ</span>
      </div>
      <strong class="endgame-stat__value">2 000 - 2 400+</strong>
    </article>

    <article class="endgame-stat">
      <div class="endgame-stat__head">
        <span class="endgame-stat__label">Bonus de degats Fusion</span>
      </div>
      <strong class="endgame-stat__value">40 - 70%+</strong>
    </article>

    <article class="endgame-stat">
      <div class="endgame-stat__head">
        <span class="endgame-stat__label">PV</span>
      </div>
      <strong class="endgame-stat__value">15 000+</strong>
    </article>

    <article class="endgame-stat">
      <div class="endgame-stat__head">
        <span class="endgame-stat__label">DEF</span>
      </div>
      <strong class="endgame-stat__value">1 100+</strong>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
